WEBVTT

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:05.910
If I hadn't changed back then with Jehovah's help, all things would be so

00:00:05.910 --> 00:00:16.859
different today. I guess I'm not the only one whose loyalty was tested, but for

00:00:16.859 --> 00:00:26.050
me it was a little more subtle. My phone was a door to just about everything, but

00:00:26.050 --> 00:00:34.409
that door opened to some places I shouldn't have gone. At first I thought it's

00:00:34.409 --> 00:00:42.570
not pornography, so it's okay, but still, what I was seeing filled my mind with

00:00:42.570 --> 00:00:53.289
immoral thoughts, and I couldn't stop. Galatians 6, 7 and 8 reads, do not be

00:00:53.289 --> 00:01:00.329
misled. God is not one to be mocked. For whatever a person is sewing, this he will

00:01:00.329 --> 00:01:13.659
also reap. Reap what you sow. Reap what you sow. I was sewing unclean desires, and

00:01:13.659 --> 00:01:27.140
reaping a double heart. De-sensitized to things Jehovah hates. Turn my eyes away

00:01:27.140 --> 00:01:33.219
from looking at what is worthless. It wasn't just whether an image is

00:01:33.219 --> 00:01:40.560
considered pornography. Anything that stirs up unclean thoughts is worthless, and I

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:52.120
should turn my eyes away. But I had to do more. Those weren't just the

00:01:52.120 --> 00:02:02.500
psalmist words. They had to be my words. Words I've had to act on ever since to

00:02:02.500 --> 00:02:05.900
stay loyal to Jehovah.
